Fiscal year 2020 results and highlights (continued):
•We increased our quarterly dividend by over 15% from $1.16 to $1.34 per share, representing the largest dividend
increase in our 80-year history. This is the 38 consecutive year that we have increased our quarterly dividend
payment.
•We successfully executed a debt offering of approximately $5 billion during the third quarter, supporting significant
opportunities to invest in high-return industrial gas projects and the repayment of upcoming debt maturities. The
issuance included both U.S. Dollar- and Euro-denominated fixed-rate notes.
